 *        SCL - A5
 *        SDA - A4
 *        VCC - 5v
 *        GND - Gnd
 *        
 *    ArbotiX
 *        LCD - ~duino Pin 
 *        SCL - D16 9Pin closest to processor0
 *        SDA - D17 9Pin closest to processor0
 *        VCC - 5v Pin on D17 (Middle Pin)
